Hello,

Would it be possible to open another mailing list only devoted to the
``Core Caml`` aspects of OCaml ? 

Being restricted to purely functional programming  topics (functions,
data types, modules, etc), this list would be lighter and reading it
would hopefully be much less time consuming.

I suggest to name it "core-caml-list".

